---
<section class="py-16 bg-brand-softBg border-b border-brand-border/30">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">Move Existing Content into a Better-Structured Kajabi System</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-textMain">We support migrations from other platforms or complete rebuilds of messy existing Kajabi accounts.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">

      <div class="lg:col-span-1 bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-brand-border shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4 border-b border-brand-border pb-3">Supported Sources</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-brand-textMain">
          <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-brand-secondary rounded-full mr-2"></span> WordPress (LearnDash/Tutor LMS)</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-brand-secondary rounded-full mr-2"></span> Teachable & Thinkific</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-brand-secondary rounded-full mr-2"></span> Google Drive & Dropbox</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-brand-secondary rounded-full mr-2"></span> Manually managed libraries</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-brand-secondary rounded-full mr-2"></span> Old Kajabi Courses & templates</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-brand-secondary rounded-full mr-2"></span> Existing Kajabi accounts needing restructuring</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-2 bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-brand-border shadow-sm">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4 border-b border-brand-border pb-3">The Migration Process</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-x-6 gap-y-3 text-sm text-brand-textMain">
          <div class="flex"><span class="font-bold text-brand-primary w-6">1.</span> Audit</div>
          <div class="flex"><span class="font-bold text-brand-primary w-6">8.</span> Offer and checkout setup</div>

          <div class="flex"><span class="font-bold text-brand-primary w-6">2.</span> Inventory</div>
          <div class="flex"><span class="font-bold text-brand-primary w-6">9.</span> Email and Automation setup</div>

          <div class="flex"><span class="font-bold text-brand-primary w-6">3.</span> Backup and export review</div>
          <div class="flex"><span class="font-bold text-brand-primary w-6">10.</span> User-access planning</div>

          <div class="flex"><span class="font-bold text-brand-primary w-6">4.</span> Content mapping</div>
          <div class="flex"><span class="font-bold text-brand-primary w-6">11.</span> Domain and redirect review</div>

          <div class="flex"><span class="font-bold text-brand-primary w-6">5.</span> Curriculum restructuring</div>
          <div class="flex"><span class="font-bold text-brand-primary w-6">12.</span> Quality assurance</div>

          <div class="flex"><span class="font-bold text-brand-primary w-6">6.</span> Website and page planning</div>
          <div class="flex"><span class="font-bold text-brand-primary w-6">13.</span> Launch and handover</div>

          <div class="flex"><span class="font-bold text-brand-primary w-6">7.</span> Product setup</div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="bg-amber-50 p-6 rounded-xl border border-amber-200 mb-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-sm text-amber-900">
      <p class="font-bold mb-2">Important Migration Considerations:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
        <li>Migration capabilities depend heavily on the source-platform's export tools.</li>
        <li>Some information, configurations, or custom code may require manual recreation.</li>
        <li>User and payment data requires careful handling—payment details must not be transferred insecurely.</li>
        <li>Exact migration scope and timelines are confirmed only after a comprehensive audit.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
      <a href="/book-free-kajabi-audit/" class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-6 py-3 border border-transparent text-base font-bold rounded-md text-white bg-brand-primary hover:bg-brand-primary/90 transition-colors shadow-sm">
        Request a Kajabi Migration Review
        <svg class="ml-2 -mr-1 w-5 h-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path></svg>
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
